## Summary

I think writing summaries for science fiction books makes not much sense, but the whole Foundation Series is simply awesome. 7 books in total, they are all worth it. And all the rest of Asimov is worth it too.

Foundation Novels in Order:

- [Foundation](/library/foundation)
- [Foundation and Empire](/library/foundation-and-empire)
- [Second Foundation](/library/foundation-second-foundation)
- [Foundation's Edge](/library/foundations-edge)
- [Foundation and Earth](/library/foundation-and-earth)

Prequels: 

- [Prelude to Foundation](/library/foundation-prelude-to-foundation) 
- [Forward the Foundation](/library/foundation-forward-the-foundation) (this book)



